OL,3,CEnergy bills set to fall as Tories and
OL,4,CLabour clash over policy
OL,6,FOfgem announced on Friday that the
OL,7,Faverage household energy bill will
OL,8,Fdrop by around 7% from July 1
OL,10,FHousehold energy bills will fall again
OL,11,Fin July but remain around 40% higher
OL,12,Fthan pre-gas crisis levels. The topic
OL,13,Fis a key focus in campaigning, which
OL,14,Fstarted on Thursday.
OL,16,Fannounced on Friday that the average
OL,17,Fhousehold energy bill will drop by
OL,18,Faround 7% from July 1 when the latest
OL,19,Fchange to the regulator's price cap
OL,20,Ftakes effect.
