OL,6,F"Families are picking up the tab of 14
OL,7,Fyears of Tory energy failure and are
OL,8,Fexpected to remain a staggering #400 a
OL,9,Fyear worse off under the new price
OL,10,Fcap."
OL,12,FEnergy Secretary Claire Coutinho set
OL,13,Fout plans for consumer-friendly
OL,14,Fchanges and accused Labour of not
OL,15,Fbeing "honest about the costs" that
OL,16,Ftheir plans for net zero power would
OL,17,Finvolve.
