OL,3,CEnergy bills set to fall as Tories and
OL,4,CLabour clash over policy
OL,6,FMs Coutinho said Labour's drive to
OL,7,Fdecarbonise the electricity system by
OL,8,F2030 would "take us back to square one
OL,9,Fby making voters pay more for net
OL,10,Fzero".
OL,12,FShe said shifting away from North Sea
OL,13,Foil and gas would put 200,000 jobs at
OL,14,Frisk.
OL,16,FHer own energy policies include
OL,17,Fmaintaining the Ofgem cap throughout
OL,18,Fthe next Parliament to help keep bills
OL,19,Fdown.
