OL,6,FMeanwhile, Sir Ed Davey said the
OL,7,FLiberal Democrats would cut energy
OL,8,Fbills by investing in home insulation
OL,9,Fand boosting renewables.
OL,11,F"Energy bills remain far higher than
OL,12,Ffive years ago, on top of sky-high
OL,13,Fmortgages and rents and prices in the
OL,14,Fshops," Sir Ed said.
OL,16,F"Families and pensioners are feeling
OL,17,Fworse off after years of Conservative
OL,18,Fchaos.
